title: Myanmar CPI Transportation
description: The transportation sub-index of the CPI basket in Myanmar increased to 195.64 points in June of 2022 from 188.03 points in May of 2022. CPI Transportation in Myanmar averaged 108.11 points from 2013 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 195.64 points in June of 2022 and a record low of 87.69 points in March of 2016. This page provides - Myanmar Cpi Transportation- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Central Statistics Organization, Myanmar
